Get officials rankings

Source: R/kp_misc_stats.R
kp_officials.Rd

Get officials rankings

kp_officials(year = most_recent_mbb_season())

Arguments

year

Year of data to pull

Value

A data frame with 7 columns:

Rk

integer.

OfficialName

character.

RefRating

double.

Gms

double.

Last.Game

character.

Last.Game.1

character.

Year

double.

Examples

# \donttest{
  try(kp_officials(year = 2021))
